summary: A small abode under the bridge in whiterun.
descriptionHtml:
This is my first mod and I think it turned out pretty well.
Its a small den under the bridge in whiterun. It dosent contain enchanting table,work bench etc partly because I wanted it to be a sort of cheap slum tipe thing. It does contain a bed,map,chair and a book about the mark on the wall.

I dont think I will update this mod because I have no reason to.
I dont know of any issues so if you find some then message me and I\'ll try my best to fix them.
I was using the vibrant fantasy enb. (go check it out)

Please leave feedback and suggestions about where you want the next den to pop up.

HOPE YOU ENJOY
author: BarronTV1
